---
title: CareerVivid - End-to-End Publishing & AI Sync Workflow
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant CLI as CareerVivid CLI
    participant MCP as AI Agent (MCP)
    box rgb(30, 27, 75) CareerVivid Cloud
        participant API as Core API Gateway
        participant Auth as Firebase Auth
        participant AI as Gemini AI Engine
        participant DB as Firestore DB
    end
    participant Web as Web/Portfolio UI

    %% Authentication Phase
    note over Dev,Auth: 1. Secure Authentication Flow
    Dev->>CLI: Runs `cv auth`
    CLI->>Auth: Initiates Browser OAuth
    Auth-->>Dev: Prompts Google/GitHub Login
    Dev->>Auth: Approves Access
    Auth-->>CLI: Returns Secure Session Token & Config

    %% Authoring & Publishing Phase
    note over Dev,DB: 2. Content Authoring & API Publishing
    Dev->>CLI: Runs `cv publish system-design.mmd`
    alt Agent-Driven Path
        Dev->>MCP: "Publish this diagram using the MCP tool"
        MCP->>API: POST /api/publish (Tool Call)
    else CLI Path
        CLI->>API: POST /api/publish (Payload w/ Token)
    end
    
    API->>API: Validates Mermaid/Markdown Syntax
    
    %% AI Enhancement (Optional)
    opt AI Enhancement Enabled
        API->>AI: Send Content for SEO Optimization
        AI-->>API: Returns Optimized Output & Tags
    end

    API->>DB: Stores Content Document
    DB-->>API: Returns Post ID & Timestamp
    API-->>CLI: 201 Created (Live URL)
    API-->>MCP: Tool Call Success (Live URL)
    
    CLI-->>Dev: Prints Success & Live Link in Terminal

    %% Viewing & Syncing Phase
    note over Dev,Web: 3. Community Distribution & Portfolio Sync
    Dev->>Web: Visits https://careervivid.app/community
    Web->>API: Fetch Latest Feed
    API->>DB: Query Recent Posts
    DB-->>API: Returns Aggregated Feed
    API-->>Web: Real-time UI Update
